This paper deals with the problem of optimizing path encoding in software-defined networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure (NI) and data centers (DC). It also involves information theory (IT) and algorithms (AL) for finding an efficient solution. Additionally, the paper mentions traffic engineering and service chaining, which are topics related to system and control (SI).
